title: Cafe Central
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, European, German, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Big restaurant in the center of town at the main street/pedestrian zone. Offers many vegetarian dishes marked with "VG," and in 2014 added a a separate full page for vegan items which includes soup and warm entrees. Food is made onsite.
